                    <item>
                <title>Charity Care</title>
                <link>
                https://www.accl.com.tw/en/modules/news/article.php?storyid=19</link>
                <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Love Activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;ACCL has participated in various peace-of-mind activities and donations since 2013, including the &quot;Children&#039;s Dream Flying Project&quot; of the Xu Chaoying Charity Foundation to care for disadvantaged children, the World Vision, the Formosa Fun Coast water park blaze, and the TPCA Environment Foundation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Community Participation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Establish friendly relations with the neighbors, regularly invite local and foreign colleagues to clean the surrounding environment of the factory, maintain the cleanliness of the neighborhood, promote environmental protection and cleanliness activities, and give back to Wulin Vil. environmental protection resource recycling vehicle donations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <pubDate>Thu, 25 Feb 2021 10:01:19 +1600</pubDate>
                <guid>https://www.accl.com.tw/en/modules/news/article.php?storyid=19</guid>
            </item>
                    <item>
                <title>Safety and Health</title>
